[gd_scene format=3 uid="uid://crafting_test_scene_0001"]

; Integration-test scene for the crafting gameplay scenario (task 3.16).
;
; The scene is intentionally a bare skeleton: three placeholder `Node`s
; that the integration test (`tests/integration/test_crafting_scenario.gd`)
; populates at runtime. The real subsystem classes — `InventorySystem`
; and `CraftingManager` — extend `RefCounted`, so they cannot be
; attached directly as scene scripts; the test instantiates them through
; `addons/forgekit_rpg/public_api.gd` and binds them to the matching
; `Node` via `set_meta`/`set` once the RPG module has been installed.
;
; Keeping the scene free of `ext_resource` references to the paid
; `addons/forgekit_rpg/**` scripts also keeps this file loadable in the
; public Core template, where the module ships only as a placeholder
; `.gitkeep` directory.

